{"type": "article", "id": 27287, "title": "尺笔合一的文具", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-25T06:32:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702132408PlE2qZebNgGwfmKn.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>来自台湾的 <a href=\"http://hmmproject.com/\">HMM</a> 设计团队一直专注于改造我们习以为常的日常用品，最近他们推出了一款便携的尺笔合一的文具。Rule/One 的尺和笔之间通过磁贴吸附在一起，侧面看就好像滴液一样，可以当作书签或镇纸使用。如果你的办公已经完全去纸化，它配备的电容笔头能让你在各类触屏设备上进行工作。这是它的<a href=\"http://hmmproject.com/products/rule-one\">购买链接</a>，售价 60 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132406Vs31Ye90fAIixCBE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.70571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132406ViAYUotfpy6TZWR8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021324070b3TtgaLRnOHF6Qd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132407YEwcUnuDgXbZmpH6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}